# Conventional Commits — <type>(<scope>): <description> (#<issue>)
#
# Types (required):  feat | fix | refactor | docs | ci | chore | test
# Scope (optional):  e.g. web, admin-ui, api, auth, ui, infra, config, 
# Issue (encouraged): (#123) at end
#
# Examples:
#   feat(web): add enrollment card component (#201)
#   fix(auth): handle session expiry on redirect (#198)
#   refactor(ui): extract table to reusable component
#   chore(infra): update docker compose ports
#
# Branch rule: <type>/<issue-number>-description  (issue required except chore)
#   feat/201-enrollment-card | fix/198-session-expiry | chore/update-docker

